				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Actually not that far off. 
<br />

<br />
1/2% of 4000 is 20, not 10.
<br />

<br />
Given that casters typically use one spell for dealing damage in a given encounter, it is completely appropriate to compare the fractional gain in available mana to the damage of a single spell. You can't cast more than one at a time, unless you are doing something that I think SOE would frown upon greatly.
<br />

<br />
It is a straight damage-potential to damage-potential comparison, and one that is close enough to well illustrate the impotence of the OoW spell lineup for mages.
<br />

<br />
"Try something else, please" I trust was directed to SOE?<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.sovereignguild.org/forum/viewtopic.php?t=4429" target="_blank" class="postlink">Master Elementalist Itchyban of Veeshan</a>
