I'm sorry, a 1/2% increase in available mana is really even more bullshit than some of the AAs we've gotten. If you can't see it conclusively in a 5- or 10-minute parse, it really doesn't matter enough.
<br />

<br />
I still consider tying the rune to damage to the pet a bad idea, though I can't immediately think of a better one (mana, for a class that is already at the bottom of the barrel for mana regen and damage ability vs. other DPS classes, is a bad choice).<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.sovereignguild.org/forum/viewtopic.php?t=4429" target="_blank" class="postlink">Master Elementalist Itchyban of Veeshan</a>
